            <lg xml:id="TK298">
<l>puṟantūymai nīrā ṉamaiyu makantūymai</l>
<l>vāymaiyāṟ kāṇap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Purity of body is produced by water and purity of mind by truthfulness.</l>
